
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Starter Demo | Love Crafted Digital</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Serif+Display&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: "Inter", system-ui, sans-serif;
      background: #0b1120;
      color: #e5e7eb;
    }
    .wrap {
      max-width: 960px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 2.5rem 1.3rem 3rem;
    }
    header {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }
    .logo-img {
      height: 44px;
      width: auto;
      display: block;
    }
    nav a {
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      color: #9ca3af;
      margin-left: 1.5rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.16em;
    }
    nav a:hover {
      color: #e5e7eb;
    }
    .hero {
      text-align: left;
      margin-bottom: 3.5rem;
    }
    h1 {
      font-family: "DM Serif Display", serif;
      font-size: clamp(2.1rem, 4vw, 2.8rem);
      margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
    }
    h1 span {
      color: #60a5fa;
    }
    .lede {
      color: #9ca3af;
      max-width: 28rem;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.8rem;
    }
    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 0.7rem 1.5rem;
      border-radius: 999px;
      border: 1px solid #60a5fa;
      background: #1d4ed8;
      color: white;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      text-decoration: none;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.16em;
    }
    .btn-secondary {
      background: transparent;
      border-color: #4b5563;
      color: #e5e7eb;
      margin-left: 0.6rem;
    }
    section {
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }
    h2 {
      font-family: "DM Serif Display", serif;
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
    }
    .services-grid {
      display: grid;
      gap: 1.2rem;
    }
    @media (min-width: 700px) {
      .services-grid {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
      }
    }
    .card {
      border-radius: 1rem;
      border: 1px solid #1f2937;
      padding: 1.1rem 1rem;
      background: radial-gradient(circle at 0 0, rgba(96,165,250,0.16), #020617);
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }
    .card-title {
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
    }
    footer {
      border-top: 1px solid #111827;
      padding-top: 1.2rem;
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      color: #6b7280;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrap">
    <header>
      <div class="logo">
        <img src="assets/logo-lovecrafted-digital.png"
             alt="Love Crafted Digital logo"
             class="logo-img">
      </div>
      <nav>
        <a href="#services">Services</a>
        <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
      </nav>
    </header>

    <main>
      <section class="hero">
        <h1>Simple, launch-ready site for small businesses.</h1>
        <p class="lede">
          A clean one-page layout that gets your business online fast—with just enough personality to feel like you.
        </p>
        <a href="#contact" class="btn">Book a consult</a>
        <a href="#services" class="btn btn-secondary">View sections</a>
      </section>

      <section id="services">
        <h2>What’s included</h2>
        <div class="services-grid">
          <article class="card">
            <div class="card-title">Home section</div>
            <p>Hero, quick overview of what you do, clear call-to-action for booking or contact.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="card">
            <div class="card-title">About & Services</div>
            <p>Short story about your brand and a simple service list with pricing or “starting at” ranges.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="card">
            <div class="card-title">Contact block</div>
            <p>Contact form or direct links to your email, phone, and social profiles.</p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="contact">
        <h2>Next steps</h2>
        <p style="color:#9ca3af; max-width:30rem; font-size:0.95rem;">
          This demo shows how a starter build can stay simple and still look professional.
          On your actual site, this section would have your real contact details and a quick inquiry form.
        </p>
      </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
      © <span id="year"></span> Love Crafted Digital — Starter Demo
    </footer>
  </div>

  <script>
    document.getElementById("year").textContent = new Date().getFullYear();
  </script>
</body>
</html>

